"6 tablespoons unsalted butter, divided","1 cup panko (Japanese breadcrumbs)","2 cups (8 oz.) shredded extra-sharp Cheddar cheese, divided","3 cups reduced-sodium, fat-free chicken broth","2 cups milk","1  bay leaf","1  fresh thyme sprig","2 cups chopped onion","1/2 cup diced celery","1  (8-oz.) package sliced cremini mushrooms","1 teaspoon kosher salt, divided","  Pinch of freshly ground black pepper","  Pinch of ground red pepper","2  garlic cloves, minced","1/4 cup all-purpose flour","1 1/2 cups uncooked long-grain rice","1/2 cup sour cream","1/2 cup mayonnaise","1/8 teaspoon freshly grated nutmeg","3 cups fresh broccoli florets (about 2 heads)"